          📥 GeoJSON (15.566 mudas)
        </a>
        <a href={`${base}planejamento`}
           class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-sm bg-terracota-700/60 hover:bg-terracota-600 text-pergaminho-100 text-sm font-mono border border-terracota-600/50 transition-all">
