        <p class="font-data text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-dado-verde/70 mb-3">Déficit Arb. Urbano Est.</p>
        <p class="font-display font-bold text-3xl text-dado-verde mb-1">0.44–1.02 km²</p>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-pergaminho-200/60">~8–18% da superfície urbana</p>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-floresta-600 mt-2">Cálculo: plano 15.566 mudas</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div data-animate class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="data-table w-full">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th class="text-left">Uso do Solo</th>
            <th class="text-center">%</th>
            <th class="text-right">Área (km²)</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td class="font-body text-sm text-floresta-400">Formação Florestal</td><td class="text-center font-mono text-xs">48.1%</td><td class="text-right font-mono text-xs">~151.0</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="font-body text-sm text-floresta-400">Formação Savânica</td><td class="text-center font-mono text-xs">0.3%</td><td class="text-right font-mono text-xs">~0.9</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="font-body text-sm text-pergaminho-200/70">Agricultura</td><td class="text-center font-mono text-xs">18.5%</td><td class="text-right font-mono text-xs">~58.1</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="font-body text-sm text-pergaminho-200/70">Pastagem</td><td class="text-center font-mono text-xs">20.1%</td><td class="text-right font-mono text-xs">~63.1</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="font-body text-sm text-terracota-400">Área Urbana</td><td class="text-center font-mono text-xs">1.8%</td><td class="text-right font-mono text-xs">~5.7</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-floresta-600">
      Contenda está na transição Floresta Ombrófila Mista ↔ Densa (Mata Atlântica).
