      <a href="https://brasil.mapbiomas.org/download/mapbiomas-colecao-8/" target="_blank" class="text-floresta-400 hover:text-terracota-400">MapBioms C8 ↗</a>
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="divider mx-6 md:mx-16"></div>

